Package us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes

Class StartpunktApplicationWrapper

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes.BaseKubernetesObject
us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes.StartpunktApplicationWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
KubernetesObject
public class StartpunktApplicationWrapper extends BaseKubernetesObject
Wrapper for Startpunkt application Kubernetes custom resources. This class extracts application-specific information from the resource's spec with fallbacks to defaults from the base class.
